        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[【[桃里桃气]爱美要理性！#医生提醒过早医美抗衰可能适得其反#】医生介绍，18岁-25岁，人体细胞活性正处于递增状态，无需进行注射、光电等医美项目的外部干预。...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【[桃里桃气]爱美要理性！<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%8C%BB%E7%94%9F%E6%8F%90%E9%86%92%E8%BF%87%E6%97%A9%E5%8C%BB%E7%BE%8E%E6%8A%97%E8%A1%B0%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E9%80%82%E5%BE%97%E5%85%B6%E5%8F%8D%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%8C%BB%E7%94%9F%E6%8F%90%E9%86%92%E8%BF%87%E6%97%A9%E5%8C%BB%E7%BE%8E%E6%8A%97%E8%A1%B0%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E9%80%82%E5%BE%97%E5%85%B6%E5%8F%8D%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#医生提醒过早医美抗衰可能适得其反#</span></a>】医生介绍，18岁-25岁，人体细胞活性正处于递增状态，无需进行注射、光电等医美项目的外部干预。医美机构为扩大消费者群体面，宣传“18岁就要抗初老”等概念以增加获利。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%85%B3%E4%BA%8E%E6%8A%97%E8%A1%B0%E8%80%81%E6%9C%89%E5%93%AA%E4%BA%9B%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E8%AF%AF%E5%8C%BA%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%85%B3%E4%BA%8E%E6%8A%97%E8%A1%B0%E8%80%81%E6%9C%89%E5%93%AA%E4%BA%9B%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E8%AF%AF%E5%8C%BA%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#关于抗衰老有哪些常见误区#</span></a>？事实上，过早进行光电治疗容易形成瘢痕，抗衰效果可能适得其反。如何科学抗衰老？戳👇🏻（央视新闻）<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:5005567916441620" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视新闻的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/orj480/002TLsr9ly1hn6inqpzuij61gx0tsqst02.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/1Nd9WRQ6lx08cPG9s69y01041200iH9N0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1708924433&amp;ssig=cdOLXmJrJ9&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/yjSp0aCSlx08cPG9Fnbq010412009GQu0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1708924433&amp;ssig=BMjlaQczxJ&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/qkIJXgxTlx08cPG8YKPS010412005O5y0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1708924433&amp;ssig=oz1oTP6uYk&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A5005567916441620" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
