            <title><![CDATA[[哆啦A梦吃惊]#空腹血糖达到多少算糖尿病#一般来说，正常人的空腹血糖（FBG）数值范围在3.9-6.1mmol/L，餐后两小时血糖小于7.8mmol/L；而空腹血糖6.1mmol/L＜FBG...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[哆啦A梦吃惊]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/doraemon/dr_01chijing-31d5542cca.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E7%A9%BA%E8%85%B9%E8%A1%80%E7%B3%96%E8%BE%BE%E5%88%B0%E5%A4%9A%E5%B0%91%E7%AE%97%E7%B3%96%E5%B0%BF%E7%97%85%23&amp;extparam=%23%E7%A9%BA%E8%85%B9%E8%A1%80%E7%B3%96%E8%BE%BE%E5%88%B0%E5%A4%9A%E5%B0%91%E7%AE%97%E7%B3%96%E5%B0%BF%E7%97%85%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#空腹血糖达到多少算糖尿病#</span></a><br><br>一般来说，正常人的空腹血糖（FBG）数值范围在3.9-6.1mmol/L，餐后两小时血糖小于7.8mmol/L；而空腹血糖6.1mmol/L＜FBG＜7mmol/L，属于空腹血糖受损。如果两次空腹血糖都≥7mmol/L，则考虑为糖尿病。<br><br>高血压、高血脂、高血糖和高尿酸什么适合吃？什么该少吃？学起来<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[干饭人]" src="https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/cb/2022_Foodie_org.png" data-rsshub-image="href" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>q（阜外深圳医院、京医通）<img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hn4e9oduvtj20n00w240i.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hn4e9ofzlvj20n00rx763.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hn4e9odgbfj20n00w2gnq.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hn4e9odimmj20n00rxq53.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
